    dc:description "Fig. 39. Cornutopria S. Endrödy-Younga, 1978: a–f – C. basilewskyi S. Endrödy-Younga, 1978. a – dorsal view of male head and first three antennomeres; b – male antennal club and antennomeres 4–11; c – mentum; d – dorsal view of aedeagus; e–f – dorsal and lateral view of male pygidium. All drawings modified from ENDRÖDY-YOUNGA (1978). Refer to ENDRÖDY-YOUNGA (1978) for scale." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/5363214/files/figure.png" ;
